WEBVTT

00:00:00.263 --> 00:00:02.294
You're probably familiar with FOMO.

00:00:02.318 --> 00:00:03.778
[This guy invented the term]

00:00:03.802 --> 00:00:05.678
That's short for "Fear Of Missing Out."

00:00:05.702 --> 00:00:06.966
It's that feeling you get

00:00:06.990 --> 00:00:09.537
when it seems everyone else
is doing something better

00:00:09.561 --> 00:00:10.868
than what you're doing now.

00:00:10.892 --> 00:00:13.078
But there's another FO
you need to know about,

00:00:13.102 --> 00:00:14.508
and it's far more dangerous.

00:00:14.532 --> 00:00:15.899
It's called FOBO,

00:00:15.923 --> 00:00:18.438
and it's short for "Fear
Of a Better Option."

00:00:18.462 --> 00:00:21.296
[The Way We Work]

00:00:22.842 --> 00:00:25.308
We live in a world of overwhelming choice.

00:00:25.332 --> 00:00:27.142
Even decisions that used to be simple,

00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:30.198
like choosing a restaurant
or making everyday purchases,